    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>In her essay "Meet Me in St. Louis, and Paris, London, Chicago . . ."  [ Dec. 12 ] , Vicki Goldberg reviewed at some length the current photography exhibition at the Gallery of the New York School of Interior Design, "The Great Age of Fairs." She failed to mention, though, that the show was curated by me, with the assistance of Sally Forbes, assistant director of the gallery. DAVID GARRARD LOWE  New York</p>
      </block>
